lead_paragraph: Chinese conglomerate Fosun, controlled by billionaire Guo Guangchang, is set to raise its bid for holiday company Club Mediterranee on Monday to trump Italian tycoon Andrea Bonomi, a source familiar with the process said.

headline.main: Fosun Set to Raise Offer in Club Med Bid Battle: Source
